OL,3,CMotorist in court accused of leaving a
OL,4,Cpedestrian with 'life-changing'
OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,FA Northumberland motorist has appeared
OL,8,Fin court accused of leaving a
OL,9,Fpedestrian with "life-changing"
OL,10,Finjuries following a collision.
OL,12,FJohn Stewart was alleged to have been
OL,13,Fdriving a van dangerously when he
OL,14,Fstruck a woman walking along Riverside
OL,15,FRoad, in Alnmouth, leaving her with
OL,16,Fcatastrophic injuries.
OL,18,FThe crash happened in the picturesque
OL,19,Fcoastal town on 5 April last year.
