OL,3,CMotorist in court accused of leaving a
OL,4,Cpedestrian with 'life-changing'
OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,FStewart, 47, of Argle Street, also in
OL,8,FAlnmouth, appeared in the dock at
OL,9,FNewcastle Magistrates' Court this week
OL,10,Fto face an allegation of causing
OL,11,Fserious injury by dangerous driving.
OL,12,FHe pleaded not guilty to the charge.
OL,14,FRuth Forster, prosecuting, said the
OL,15,Ffemale pedestrian had been left with
OL,16,F"life-changing" injuries following the
OL,17,Fcollision.
OL,19,FShe added: "This is not suitable to be
OL,20,Fheard here - the starting point, if
OL,21,Fconvicted, is two years in custody."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
