OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,F"If you don't attend, a warrant will
OL,8,Fbe issued for your arrest and an
OL,9,Fabsconding charge will be laid against
OL,10,Fyou.
OL,12,F"The case is also likely to go ahead
OL,13,Fin your absence. It's important you
OL,14,Fstay in touch with your solicitor."
OL,16,FStewart was released on conditional
OL,17,Fbail to next appear before Newcastle
OL,18,FCrown Court on 9 October.
